to acknowledge it or not.

00:09:13.720 --> 00:09:17.560 align:middle line:84%
Free will is a constant,
and it is omnipresent.

00:09:17.560 --> 00:09:19.790 align:middle line:90%
So all of us have free will.

00:09:19.790 --> 00:09:24.280 align:middle line:84%
It's just a matter of what
we choose to do with it.

00:09:24.280 --> 00:09:28.360 align:middle line:84%
The third is not
violating another being,

00:09:28.360 --> 00:09:30.340 align:middle line:90%
