00:09:48.290 --> 00:09:51.320 align:middle line:84%
And once we start, to
the best of our ability,

00:09:51.320 --> 00:09:54.490 align:middle line:84%
not violating another
being's free will,

00:09:54.490 --> 00:09:57.070 align:middle line:84%
