00:10:21.960 --> 00:10:23.310 align:middle line:90%
So do you see?

00:10:23.310 --> 00:10:26.180 align:middle line:84%
What we're doing is
actually growing up

00:10:26.180 --> 00:10:30.740 align:middle line:84%
in our spiritual maturity to be
able to be a vibrational match

00:10:30.740 --> 00:10:34.730 align:middle line:84%
to all of those other spiritual
and higher vibrational

00:10:34.730 --> 00:10:40.040 align:middle line:84%
experiences that we
want for our world.

00:10:40.040 --> 00:10:44.210 align:middle line:84%
So to really be clear
about what natural law is,

00:10:44.210 --> 00:10:48.380 align:middle line:84%
every individual is spiritually
sovereign and, therefore,

00:10:48.380 --> 00:10:54.710 align:middle line:84%
accountable for their actions
and also for their non-actions,

00:10:54.710 --> 00:10:58.970 align:middle line:84%
for their apathy
as well as whatever

00:10:58.970 --> 00:11:04.100 align:middle line:84%
is motivating us from our
shadow or unconscious reasoning.

00:11:04.100 --> 00:11:09.280 align:middle line:84%
What this does is create what
we know as the force of karma.

00:11:09.280 --> 00:11:12.060 align:middle line:84%
Karma is the
mechanism that holds

00:11:12.060 --> 00:11:18.180 align:middle line:84%
us accountable through the
feedback loop of natural law.

00:11:18.180 --> 00:11:21.850 align:middle line:84%
Natural law and karma
are one and the same.

00:11:21.850 --> 00:11:24.790 align:middle line:84%
They are extensions
of one another.

00:11:24.790 --> 00:11:26.850 align:middle line:84%
So when we're talking
about natural law

00:11:26.850 --> 00:11:31.690 align:middle line:84%
through the extension and the
emphasis of it being as karma,

00:11:31.690 --> 00:11:33.930 align:middle line:84%
what we're really
seeing is that karma

00:11:33.930 --> 00:11:36.400 align:middle line:90%
is playing a guiding force.

00:11:36.400 --> 00:11:39.730 align:middle line:84%
It's not always punishing us,
and it's not always an enemy.

00:11:39.730 --> 00:11:42.450 align:middle line:10%
It is acting as
the guiding force

00:11:42.450 --> 00:11:46.800 align:middle line:10%
for us to understand
natural law and for us

00:11:46.800 --> 00:11:50.100 align:middle line:10%
to align with
correct action, which

00:11:50.100 --> 00:11:53.460 align:middle line:10%
would be to align with
our ability not to invade

00:11:53.460 --> 00:11:56.310 align:middle line:10%
another person's free will.

00:11:56.310 --> 00:12:00.480 align:middle line:84%
