whether it's mainstream
or in mysticism,

00:12:30.470 --> 00:12:36.100 align:middle line:84%
are all referring to by the
name The Golden Rule, which is,

00:12:36.100 --> 00:12:40.630 align:middle line:84%
do unto others as you would
have them do unto you.

00:12:40.630 --> 00:12:44.500 align:middle line:84%
This is the simplest way
to understand natural law,

00:12:44.500 --> 00:12:47.630 align:middle line:84%
and that's what karma
is in a nutshell.

