then unconsciousness would
be linked to separation,

00:13:12.440 --> 00:13:18.210 align:middle line:84%
and it would be linked to chaos
and even lower vibratory states.

00:13:18.210 --> 00:13:20.480 align:middle line:84%
And so I want to really
make this distinction

00:13:20.480 --> 00:13:22.640 align:middle line:84%
when it comes to
natural law, how

00:13:22.640 --> 00:13:27.500 align:middle line:84%
aligning with it creates
and produces love and order,

00:13:27.500 --> 00:13:33.000 align:middle line:84%
and not aligning with it
creates separation, fear, chaos,

00:13:33.000 --> 00:13:35.390 align:middle line:90%
and even control.

